{"id":"8457779e-cda0-420a-9119-24cd2cc06472","name":"Sothis, The Beginning","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(24, 183, 111);\">Sothis is the Progenitor God of Fódlan, and the mysterious girl you've been seeing in your dreams. An amnesiac known as The Beginning, she resides inside your consciousness.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Appears in </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 134, 34);\"><strong>Fire Emblem:</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(145, 79, 199);\"><strong>Three Houses</strong>.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/x58P-Wljw4jQyhBIpGLOJ.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116);\">(Please leave reviews if I can improve the character or if you enjoy the character. Your ratings give me endorphins.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">UPDATE 10/1: A Three Houses lorebook has been added, so now you can properly insert yourself into the world of Fódlan if you so desire!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/v2Gpt8t-wxeWKtgIpDMFg.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em>RECOMMENDED BOT LINKS:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/34751ce5-7d7d-4130-83f2-c12c36e8ac35_character-camilla-bewitching-princess\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Camilla</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong> </strong></span>- Your older sister and the bewitching elder princess of Nohr from Fire Emblem Fates.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2e8fb3c9-8894-44d2-9ad7-04e063d100c5_character-tiki-nagas-voice\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Tiki</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong> </strong></span>- The daughter of the Divine Dragon and rests atop the Great Mila Tree from Fire Emblem Awakening.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/09577679-9e6a-4009-88b3-257a1eaaa32c_character-freyja-lady-of-nightmare\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Freyja</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span>- The Goddess of Love and ruler of the realm of nightmares from Fire Emblem Heroes.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/86ca4323-5b12-499a-afaa-8b5d422e1517_character-lysithea-von-ordelia\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Lysithea</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span>- A daughter of a noble house and magical prodigy of the Golden Deer House from Fire Emblem: Three Houses.</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"qBwIyjbPzfvb_EU5MLG7x.webp","creator":"HouseOrdelia","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🔮 Magical"],"chats":1253,"messages":26133,"created_at":"2024-01-24T14:21:12.788291+00:00"}